                            <comment id="13561790" author="steffkes" created="Thu, 24 Jan 2013 17:39:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have no clue why, but &lt;tt&gt;form.elements&lt;/tt&gt; seems to be &lt;tt&gt;undefined&lt;/tt&gt; so, we use the semantic option (which uses &lt;tt&gt;form.getElementsByTagName(&apos;*&apos;)&lt;/tt&gt; under the hood, this is slightly slower, but does in fact the same job)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
