                            <comment id="13570001" author="dsmiley" created="Mon, 4 Feb 2013 05:41:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;For the record, the symptom is seen in Safari too &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/sad.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
(I haven&apos;t tested the patch but someone on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4393&quot; title=&quot;&amp;#39;Execute Query&amp;#39; in the dashboard does not build the url correctly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-4393&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-4393&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; says that this patch fixes it). &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13589779" author="felixbuenemann" created="Thu, 28 Feb 2013 18:43:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I saw the same problem in Safari 6.0.2 on OS X 10.8.2 and the attached patch works.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
